data.description: ASK ABOUT THE 2/1 BUY DOWN or $12,000 in Closing Costs!  Offering 4 bedrooms/3 bathrooms, this home features a spacious fenced backyard with a deck great for entertaining guests - Outdoor entertainment television and protective cover included. As you step inside, the welcoming ambiance invites you in with open arms. Admire exquisite white quartz countertops with luxurious gold finishes, a five-burner slide-in gas range with an air-fryer, a GE CAFE French door refrigerator in matte white, and a fingerprint-resistant ENERGY STAR Refrigerator. A Wash-tower stacked smart laundry system and various other modern appliances further enhance this beautiful home. The owner suite is a sight to behold that sits in separate quarters of the home and offers spacious luxury, by "California Closets", walk-in, and a beautiful spa-like bathroom featuring a frameless glass shower. Two additional secondary bedrooms and upgraded guest bathrooms offer further comfort and convenience. This home boasts a new HVAC system and has already been appraised, making this an opportunity to walk in with equity. Do not miss the opportunity to make this stunning home your own! A 3-D virtual tour is available: https://my.matterport.com/show/?m=HMyjg8rQtry
